Package eu.dzhw.fdz.metadatamanagement.common.domain.validation

package eu.dzhw.fdz.metadatamanagement.common.domain.validation
This package contains the validation annotations with the depending constrain validators of the domain objects.
Author:
Daniel Katzberg
